---
const credentials = [
  { value: '+10 años', label: 'Consultoría estratégica' },
  { value: '+7 años', label: 'Experiencia comercial' },
  { value: '+5 años', label: 'Ecommerce y Marketing' },
];
---

<section id="sobre-mi" class="bg-background py-12 md:py-24 lg:py-32">
  <div class="container-tight md:grid md:grid-cols-2 md:items-center md:gap-12">
    <div class="reveal relative">
      <div class="absolute -inset-4 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-secondary/20 via-secondary/5 to-tertiary/20 blur-2xl"></div>
      <div class="relative mx-auto w-full max-w-md rounded-2xl border border-primary/20 bg-primary p-5 shadow-xl">
        <img
          src="/perfil.png"
          alt="Matías Laporta"
          class="aspect-square w-full rounded-xl object-cover"
        />
        <a
          href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/matias-laporta/"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="mt-5 inline-flex w-full items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-accent/50 bg-white/5 px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-background transition hover:border-secondary hover:bg-secondary/10 hover:text-secondary"
        >
          <svg class="h-5 w-5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
            <path d="M20.45 20.45h-3.55v-5.57c0-1.33-.02-3.04-1.85-3.04-1.85 0-2.13 1.45-2.13 2.94v5.67H9.37V9h3.41v1.56h.05c.48-.9 1.64-1.85 3.38-1.85 3.61 0 4.28 2.38 4.28 5.47v6.27ZM5.34 7.43a2.06 2.06 0 1 1 0-4.12 2.06 2.06 0 0 1 0 4.12ZM7.12 20.45H3.56V9h3.56v11.45ZM22.22 0H1.77C.79 0 0 .77 0 1.72v20.56C0 23.23.79 24 1.77 24h20.45c.98 0 1.78-.77 1.78-1.72V1.72C24 .77 23.2 0 22.22 0Z"/>
          </svg>
          Ver mi experiencia en LinkedIn
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="reveal mt-10 md:mt-0">
      <span class="px-4 py-1 rounded-full bg-primary/5 border border-primary/10 text-primary text-sm font-bold inline-block mb-4 uppercase tracking-wider">Sobre mí</span>
      <h2 class="font-display text-3xl font-bold leading-tight text-primary sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl">
        Experiencia corporativa. <span class="text-secondary [text-shadow:_0_0_20px_rgba(243,205,116,0.3)]">Metodología ágil.</span>
      </h2>

      <p class="mt-8 mb-6 text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-600">
        Soy Matías Laporta, Asesor Consultivo. Combino una década de trayectoria en consultoría estratégica, un dominio profundo de Inteligencia Artificial y automatización. Conozco los procesos de los negocios B2B y B2C, por lo que implemento estrategias basada en experiencias reales.
      </p>

      <p class="text-lg font-semibold leading-relaxed text-primary">
        No vendo plantillas, diseño ecosistemas integrales de crecimiento predecible.
      </p>

      <dl class="mt-10 grid grid-cols-3 gap-4 border-t border-primary/10 pt-6">
        {credentials.map((c) => (
          <div>
            <dt class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-primary sm:text-3xl">{c.value}</dt>
            <dd class="mt-1 text-xs leading-snug text-gray-500 sm:text-sm">{c.label}</dd>
          </div>
        ))}
      </dl>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
